{ This is a very positional line. It should be clear that White intends to play with short castling.   6.a3  is a rare line played by the Worl Champion Magnus Carlsen. It can be found in chapter 25, starting from here. }
6... e5 { Here again, I prefer to play with the e7-e5 plan. } 7. Nf3
