{ 12.Nxg7+?  is bad in view of  12...Kf8  13.Nf5  Nxe4-+  . } 12... exf4
{ Out of the many possible moves, this is the one I prefer. } 13. Qxf4 Bxc3 14.
bxc3 Qa5 { Black has enough counterplay. } *

