18... exd5 19. Qxd5 { Now Black has a few different ways to make a draw. }
19... Nh6 { Protecting the f7-square. } 20. Qe6+ Kf8 21. Rxd6 Qe3+ 22. Rd2
{ A very difficult defense to find!   But not  22.Kb1?  because of  22...Re8  23.Qd7  Qxe4  and Black wins. }
22... Re8 23. Qd6+ Re7 24. Qd8+ Re8 { With a draw. } *

[Event "?"]
