8. Be2 { The main theoretical move.   8.h3  Nf6  transposes to 6. h3. } 8...
Qb6 { An important move! } 9. Bxg4 Bxg4 10. Qxg4 Qxd4 11. Qe2
{ The best try.   In case of  11.Be3  Qb4  now bad is  12.O-O-O?  in view of  12...Ne5  .  The threat of ...Nc4 is very unpleasant for White. }
11... Rc8 { It is very important to create immediate threats. } 12. Be3
