14... Nc6 15. Qg4 { A very strange move, but Black should be accurate. } 15...
e6 16. Nd5 h5 { Clearly the best defense. } 17. Qh3 Qb5
{ For now the b5-square is the safest. } 18. Nb6
{ If  18.Bb6  then  18...Qc4!  when Black has a lot of threats. } 18... Rd8 19.
a4 Qa5 20. Qc3 { White should go already for an endgame. } 20... Qxc3 21. Bxc3
h4 { The chances are equal. } *

