12. O-O-O { I see no good alternative to this move. } 12... Nc6 13. Nxc6
{ 13.Nb3  Qb6  is not dangerous at all. } 13... bxc6 14. Bc4
{ Now Black must remember an important knight maneuver. } 14... Nd7 15. h4 g4
{ The entire point! } 16. Qxg4 Ne5 17. Qe2 Nxc4 18. Qxc4 Be6
{ Black has very nice counterplay for the pawn. } *

