11... O-O
{ A very rare line. It leads to great complications, but I think Black is fine. Another good thing about this move is that it is new and White must also be very precise.   The main theoretical continuation is  11...Qb6  12.O-O-O  Nc6  13.Nxc6  Qxc6  . }
