{ One of the most popular systems against the Najdorf, considered to be the most positional approach.  Many great players had this move as their main weapon against the Najdorf. }
6... e5
{ The main move.  6...e6  would lead to Scheveningen type of positions.  6...e5  is the most popular move these days, and almost all top players prefer it. }
