1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. f3
{ This system has been around for ages. White wants to postpone the development of the queen's knight in order to play c4 first. }
5... e5
{ The most principled continuation. Another decent option is  5...Nc6  6.c4  e6  . }
6. Nb3 d5
{ This move feels so natural. The alternatives are  6...a5  ,  6...Be6  and  6...Nc6  . }
