Bxc5 11. Nxc6
{ The endgame after  11.Qxc6+  Qxc6  12.Nxc6  dxe4  13.Nc3  f5=  looks very equal. }
11... Nf6
{ The best move. White has many open checks, but none of them are dangerous. }
