6. Qe2 Nc6 7. c3 e6 { It is very similar tothe 6.Re1 line. } 8. d4 cxd4 9. cxd4
d5 10. e5 Ne4 11. Be3 { The main move. White prepares Ne1 and then f3. } 11...
Be7 12. Ne1 f6 { Better than ...f5. } 13. f3 Ng5
{ The only square for the knight. } 14. Nd3 O-O 15. Nd2 a5
