6. Nc3 Nc6 7. Nd5 { Starting with this move is a little strange. } 7... Be7 8.
d3 Bd8 9. O-O Nge7
{ Black is doing fine. We were following the game Naiditsch,A @@StartBracket@@2652@@EndBracket@@ - Georgiev,K @@StartBracket@@2663@@EndBracket@@, Liepaja 2007 }
