Nf6 7. Nc3 Bb4 { The position is quite similar to the Four Knights opening. }
8. Nxc6 dxc6 { I believe the endgame should be equal. } 9. Qxd8+ Kxd8 10. f3
Be6
{ The plan is quite easy: ...Ke7 and then ...Nf6-d7 followed by ...Ne5 or ...Nc5. }
