{ In case of  9.e5  Black is fine after  9...Ng4  10.f4  Bd7!  Threatening ...dxe5. }
9... O-O 10. a4 { The modern approach. } 10... Bd7
{ A rare but good move. Black just wants to bring the rook to c8. In the game Anton Guijarro, D @@StartBracket@@2679@@EndBracket@@ -Donchenko, A @@StartBracket@@2668@@EndBracket@@ Wijk aan Zee 2021, White had small pressure after  10...Be6  11.Qd1  Rc8  12.Nd5  Qd7  13.Re1  Rfe8  14.c3  += }
11. a5 Ng4 { The point of Black's play! } 12. Qb4 Rc8
{ Black has a very strong initiative. } 13. h3 Bxc3
{ This is exactly what Black was aiming for. } 14. bxc3 Ne5
{ With a very strong counterplay. } *

