[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "37) Various Second Moves "]
[Black "2.Be2 Nc6 3.f4"]
[Result "*"]

1. e4 c5 2. Be2
{ A weird move. White's idea is to continue the development with f4 and Nf3. }
2... Nc6 3. f4
{ Black can choose from many different plans. The one I prefer is to immediately attack White's center. }
3... d5 4. d3 e6
{ I think playing without ...g6 is preferable against White's chosen setup. Black wants to continue with ...Bd6 and ...Nge7. }
5. Nf3 Bd6 6. O-O Nge7 7. c3 f6 { Preventing e5. } 8. Be3 O-O
{ Black has an easy game. The plan is easy: ...Qc7, then ...b6 followed by ...Bb7. }
*

