Be6 9. Bxf6 Bxf6 10. Qd3 Nc6
{ This move is also very popular   Better is:  10...Be7 } 11. O-O-O Qb6
{ Very passive is:  11...Nd4  12.Nxd4  exd4  13.Nd5  Bxd5  14.exd5⩲ } 12. Rhf1
