13... Rfd8 14. Nd5
{ There is one very interesting idea here:  14.Bg4!?  Bxg4?  Is bad in view of  15.Nd5  Qb5  16.Nxf6+  gxf6  17.Qg3± }
14... Bxd5 15. Qxd5 Ne7 16. Qa5 Qc6 17. Bf3 Rac8 18. c3 { Better was  18.Qd2 }
