20. Na5 Ng6 { ...Be7 is the threat. } 21. Rd5 { Tougher was  21.Qa3 } 21... Nf4
22. Rd2 Be7 23. g3 Ne6 24. Bg4 Re8 { It is very difficult to stop d5 now } 25.
Rd5 Rb8 26. Nb3 Nc7 27. Rd2 a5 { A very nice tactic! Black wins. } 28. Qxa5
{ 28.Nxa5  d5-+ } 28... Qb7 { There are so many threats. } 29. Bd1 Ra8 30. Qb4
